生产国，约占新开采钯金供应的40%。俄罗斯黄金被伦敦市场拒之门外 所有黄金冶炼商的认证资格均被暂停"},"attached_info":"CkEIlvqH9sa3+qsNEAMaCDc3OTkxNTUyIIrwmpEGMAM4lAFAFGgAcgk1MjA2OTM4NzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"201 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8e05d06a698165bac01aa9a267f94e5_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1646989903.1831155","card_id":"Q_448957986","target":{"id":448957986,"title":"2022 年考研国家线公布，多学科分数线大涨，你过线了吗？复试该怎么准备？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/448957986","type":"question","created":1615538008,"answer_count":85,"follower_count":194,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4287,33814,45333,731841,1321755],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"3月11日，教育部公布了 2022 考研国家线，挺突然的，你现在是什么心情，过线了吗？ 扩散周知！2022年考研国家线公布"},"attached_info":"CkEIlvqH9sa3+qsNEAMaCDYyMDQ3MzgzINjOrIIGMAE4wgFAFWgAcgk0NDg5NTc5ODZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"197 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-b3fd681a6a212b4cb7eeb0dd1d22d758_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1646989903.18372","card_id":"Q_521280979","target":{"id":521280979,"title":"苹果、微软等 59 家在俄外企登上「国有化名单」，会给这些公司带来什么影响？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/521280979","type":"question","created":1646966094,"answer_count":69,"follower_count":213,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[922,5548,34688,37932,136525],"comment_count":11,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"俄罗斯《消息报》10日报道称，俄“社会消费倡议”组织负责人奥列格·帕夫洛夫表示，俄政府和总检察院已收到一份名单，共列出59家由于停止在俄经营或撤出俄市场而可能面临国有化的外国公司。这份名单包括大众、苹果、宜家、微软、IBM、壳牌、麦当劳、保时捷、丰田、H&M等公司。帕夫洛夫表示，该名单处于“开放状态”，还有一些在俄外国公司会被列入。这些公司的负债总额超过6万亿卢布，相当于它们过去3年在俄收入总和。据俄《生意人报》10日报道，俄安全会议副主席梅德